   <!-- Modal content -->
   <div class="modal-content">
      <span class="close">×</span>
      <h5 class="custom-h5">Changes</h5>
      <ul class="custom-list">
         <li>Optimized for jukebox keypad</li>
         <li>Modified Scoring Function</li>
         <li>Optimized system stability</li>
         <li>Reduced volume output</li>
      </ul>
      <h5 class="custom-h5">Instructions</h5>
      <h5 class="custom-h5-2">
         (Note: Unit must be connected to a TV for this process)
      </h5>
      <ul class="custom-list">
         <li>Prepare a USB flash drive (formatted to FAT32)</li>
         <li>Download the firmware</li>
         <li>
            Extract the downloaded file, you will find 2 files (aprom_SD.bin and
            aprom_TD.bin)
         </li>
         <li>Copy both files to the USB flash drive</li>
         <li>Turn off the karaoke unit</li>
         <li>Remove the Micro SD card from the karaoke unit</li>
         <li>Insert the USB flash drive into the karaoke unit</li>
         <li>Power on the karaoke unit</li>
         <li>A prompt for firmware update will appear; select "O"</li>
         <li>Wait until programming finish</li>
         <li>After the installation the unit will automatically reboot</li>
         <li>
            Another prompt for firmware update will appear; this time, choose
            "X"
         </li>
         <li>Power off the karaoke unit</li>
         <li>Reinsert the Micro SD card</li>
         <li>Power on the karaoke unit</li>
         <li>Finish</li>
      </ul>
   </div>
</div>
